These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, old-henry, davidoff
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily, dahlia
There are 3 different nationalities: british, turkish, polish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, superhero, thriller
1. the person who growslily is the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the british is the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
6. the davidoff-smoker is the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the polish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar      | davidoff  | cain       | old-henry   |
| Flower          | dahlia | marigold | lily |
| Nationality         | british  | polish | turkish    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | horror       | superhero      |

