.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
City: prague, hamburg, edinburgh
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, police-officer, pilot
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, havana, bluemaster
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, amaryllis
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the journalist is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
4. the pilot is on the left of the police-officer##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| City          | prague      | hamburg  | edinburgh        |
| Job         | pilot | police-officer | journalist |
| Cigar   | dunhill | havana | bluemaster       |
| Flower           | amaryllis     | balloon-flower     | begonia      |

