.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
City: boston, hamburg, berlin
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, hiking, gardening
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis, begonia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, game, baccarat
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| City      | hamburg    | boston        | berlin |
| Hobby           | hiking    | gardening | puzzles    |
| Flower   | lily | begonia             | amaryllis  |
| Cigar     | baccarat     | alhambra                | game  |

