.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different games are played: domino, monopoly, billiard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, sailing, basketball
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, water
House: victorian, craftsman, tower
1. the tower house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person playing domino is the tower house##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Game          | monopoly    | billiard  | domino      |
| Sport           | basketball    | ice-hockey | sailing |
| Beverage   | water   | mirinda  | soy-milk     |
| House   | victorian | craftsman    | tower      |

