.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
House: ranch-style, wooden, craftsman
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, thai, egyptian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, begonia
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, airplane
1. the person who growsbellflower is the thai##1
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the egyptian is the craftsman house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the ranch-style house##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is the nigerian##1
7. the thai is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| House         | craftsman | ranch-style     | wooden   |
| Nationality           | egyptian       | thai   | nigerian     |
| Flower   | marigold     | bellflower | begonia |
| Transport           | airplane      | jet-ski         | car  |

