City: paris, boston, venice
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, march, april
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch, british
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the british##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Cigar          | ritmeester | swisher       | bluemaster |
| City   | venice     | paris       | boston   |
| Birthday           | march      | october       | april     |
| Nationality         | egyptian   | dutch | british  |

