.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, pumpkin, orange
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, july
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, architect, dressmaker
House: farmhouse, cottage, colonial
1. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
2. the dressmaker is the colonial house##1
3. the person eating orange is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the farmhouse house is the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Food         | pumpkin   | orange | avocado |
| Birthday   | september | july         | august       |
| Job           | mechanic      | dressmaker      | architect         |
| House     | cottage      | colonial         | farmhouse          |

