.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, blueberry, kiwi
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, azalea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, house, blues
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
2. the fan of house is on the far right##1
3. the person eating blueberry is the person drinking juice##1
4. the person who growsaconite is the fan of blues##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Food       | blueberry            | nectarine      | kiwi  |
| Flower         | azalea | aconite | sunflower |
| Music-Genre         | metal               | blues | house |
| Beverage   | juice             | soy-milk       | mirinda      |

