.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
3 different games are played: whist, snooker, chess
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, drawing, magic-tricks
House: futuristic, cottage, modern
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, apricot, lavender
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Game           | chess | whist         | snooker |
| Hobby   | photography      | drawing | magic-tricks     |
| House   | futuristic   | cottage       | modern     |
| Color           | lavender    | apricot         | lilac        |

