.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, apricot, peach
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, december
3 different games are played: chess, canasta, domino
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, electronic, soul
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person playing chess##1
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating peach##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Food           | apricot | peach | eggplant |
| Birthday   | december        | july       | may     |
| Game   | canasta     | domino         | chess     |
| Music-Genre     | soul | electronic          | blues      |

