3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
