The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, august, july
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, drama, animation
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Transport         | ship | taxi | jet-ski   |
| Birthday           | july     | october    | august   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama         | animation    | western   |
| Cigar         | alhambra       | ritmeester | swisher |

