.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-14::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, d&b, soul
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, rat
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, azalea, balloon-flower
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, lilac
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the fan of d&b is the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the fan of soul is the person who likes lilac##1
6. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre    | folk | d&b     | soul      |
| Pet        | ferret | lizard       | rat |
| Flower       | azalea | daisy | balloon-flower  |
| Color   | mauve    | blood-red   | lilac  |

