.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, superhero
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, weightlifting
3 different pets are kept: goat, bird, rat
3 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, bridge
1. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero | documentary | mystery       |
| Sport          | weightlifting     | rowing   | snowboarding       |
| Pet         | goat  | rat   | bird |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | bridge       | snooker  |

