.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-16::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, chess
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, cycling
There 3 different types of food: carrot, peas, raspberry
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, coffee
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating peas is the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game         | mah-jongg     | chess | backgammon |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | cycling | skiing       |
| Food   | peas    | carrot       | raspberry     |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate | coffee       | fanta    |

