.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, badminton, snowboarding
3 different games are played: poker, domino, whist
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, roller, car
3 different pets are kept: rat, pony, hedgehog
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Sport      | snowboarding      | badminton    | parkour    |
| Game          | whist         | domino    | poker   |
| Transport           | tram | car | roller |
| Pet   | hedgehog         | rat     | pony    |

