.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, bridge
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, goldfish
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, dancing
City: colone, berlin, edinburgh
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person playing bridge is the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person playing whist##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Game      | whist         | bridge     | canasta     |
| Pet           | frog        | goldfish | rabbit |
| Hobby   | chess        | dancing   | skydiving    |
| City         | edinburgh | colone   | berlin |

