.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go
House: futuristic, farmhouse, modern
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, scientist, architect
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, dog
1. the person playing go is on the far left##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the architect is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Game          | go     | mah-jongg    | bridge    |
| House         | futuristic | modern | farmhouse     |
| Job   | dressmaker  | scientist      | architect        |
| Pet         | guinea-pig   | rabbit   | dog |

 